<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Erkinger von Seinsheim zu Hohenkottenheim</head><p>Makulierter Teilentwurf des übernächsten Briefs.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_5" id="2v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_5_r1l1">Erkingern von Sawnheim</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l2">cʒu kottenheim</ab>
</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_5_r1l3"> <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Erkinger 
<del rend="strikethrough">n von Sawnſheim </del> / Als vvir ew nehſt bey dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l4">Hanſen Mawrer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dıener <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd empoten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l5">von der habe wegen die Jr aufgehalten vnd gen kottenheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l7"> <expan>getrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / Alſo ſenden vvir 
<add><ab facs="#facs_5_r1l6"><expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> </ab></add> cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> Chuncʒen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l8"><expan>Beh<ex>eim</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener mit euch dauon cʒu reden / vnd <expan>Bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l9">vvaʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> diener in <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſache etc vt in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> </ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_5" id="2v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Erkingern von Sawnheim czu Kottenheim </del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Erkinger, als wir ew
                            nehst bey dem Hansen Mawrer, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener,
                                    <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und empoten
                                    <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> als von der habe wegen, die ir
                            aufgehalten und gen Kottenheim <expan>getrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt,
                            also senden wir <add><expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan></add> czu
                                    <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> Chunczen
                                <expan>Beh<ex>eim,</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, mit euch davon czu reden, und
                                    <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., waz der
                                    <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener in
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> sache etc. ut in
                                    <expan>for<ex>ma.</ex></expan>
</del></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
